text: Monster High is an animated television series. ==Premise== The series follows Frankie Stein, Draculaura and Clawdeen Wolf, the respective children of Frankenstein, Dracula and a Werewolf, as well as other children of famous mythical monsters they navigate the hilarity of high school in the hallowed halls of Monster High. ==Cast== *Gabrielle Nevaeh Green as Clawdeen Wolf *Iris Menas as Frankie Stein *Courtney Lin as Draculaura *Tom Revolori as Deuce Gorgon ==References== Category:2020s American animated television series Category:2022 American television series debuts
title: Monster High (TV series)
